===Intransitive verb===
'''doze'''

# to [[sleep]] [[lightly]] or briefly; to [[nap]]
#: ''I didn’t sleep very well, but I think I may have '''dozed''' a bit.''

===Noun===
'''doze'''

# {{countable}} a light, short sleep or nap
#: ''I felt much better after a short '''doze'''.''

